[
  {
    "startTime": 11.6,
    "endTime": 17.759999999999998,
    "text": "Eighteen years had come and gone"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.76,
    "endTime": 20.590000000000003,
    "text": "For Momma they flew by"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.59,
    "endTime": 23.82,
    "text": "But for me they drug on and on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.82,
    "endTime": 26.48,
    "text": "We were loadin' up that Chevy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.48,
    "endTime": 29.88,
    "text": "Both tryin' not to cry"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.88,
    "endTime": 35.56,
    "text": "Momma kept on talkin', puttin' off goodbye"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.56,
    "endTime": 41.33,
    "text": "Then she took my hand and said"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.33,
    "endTime": 46.53,
    "text": "”Baby don't forget”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.53,
    "endTime": 51.34,
    "text": "”Before you hit the highway"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.34,
    "endTime": 53.67,
    "text": "You better stop for gas"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.67,
    "endTime": 56.95,
    "text": "And there's a fifty in the ashtray"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.95,
    "endTime": 59.690000000000005,
    "text": "In case you run short on cash”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.69,
    "endTime": 62.48,
    "text": "”Here's a map and here's a Bible"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.48,
    "endTime": 67.39,
    "text": "If you ever lose your way"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.4,
    "endTime": 72.26,
    "text": "Just one more thing before you leave"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.26,
    "endTime": 88.30000000000001,
    "text": "Don't forget to remember me”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.3,
    "endTime": 91.17,
    "text": "This downtown apartment"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.17,
    "endTime": 93.98,
    "text": "Sure makes me miss home"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.98,
    "endTime": 96.91000000000001,
    "text": "And those bills there on the counter"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.91,
    "endTime": 100.67,
    "text": "Keep tellin' me I'm on my own"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.67,
    "endTime": 103.3,
    "text": "And just like every Sunday"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.3,
    "endTime": 105.75,
    "text": "I called Mama up last night"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.75,
    "endTime": 108.94,
    "text": "And even when it's not"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.94,
    "endTime": 112.25,
    "text": "I tell her everything's all right"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.25,
    "endTime": 117.37,
    "text": "Before we hung up I said"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.37,
    "endTime": 122.7,
    "text": "“Hey Mama don't forget”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.7,
    "endTime": 127.39,
    "text": "”To tell my baby sister"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.4,
    "endTime": 130.70000000000002,
    "text": "I'll see her in the fall"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.7,
    "endTime": 133.7,
    "text": "And tell Mee-Mal that I miss her"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.7,
    "endTime": 136.17999999999998,
    "text": "Yeah I should give her a call”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.18,
    "endTime": 139.23000000000002,
    "text": "”And make sure you tell daddy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.23,
    "endTime": 143.429,
    "text": "That I'm still his little girl"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.43,
    "endTime": 148.98000000000002,
    "text": "Yeah I still feel like I'm where I'm supposed to be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.98,
    "endTime": 165.85899999999998,
    "text": "But don't forget to remember me”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.86,
    "endTime": 170.62,
    "text": "Tonight I find myself kneelin' by the bed to pray"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.62,
    "endTime": 173.17000000000002,
    "text": "I haven't done this in a while"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.17,
    "endTime": 177.32,
    "text": "So I don't know what to say"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.32,
    "endTime": 180.6,
    "text": "But Lord I feel so small sometimes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.6,
    "endTime": 184.0,
    "text": "In this big old place"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.0,
    "endTime": 189.37,
    "text": "Yeah I know there's more important things"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.37,
    "endTime": 198.3,
    "text": "But don't forget to remember me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.3,
    "endTime": 208.86,
    "text": "Don't forget to remember me"
  }
]